A Virtual Research Environment specifically conceived to provide its users 
with an environment to experience with data analytics facilities. In 
particular, users of this VRE are provided with a number of ready-to-use 
algorithms and methods including data clustering (e.g. DBScan, KMeans). In 
addition to that they are provided with RStudio for developing new R-based 
analytics methods.
